      "overview_item_data": {
        "overview_item_data_type": "list",
        "overview_item_data_items": [
          "I can combine like terms to simplify linear expressions and determine their sums and differences.",
          "I can compare unknown quantities on a number line and use algebraic expressions to solve real-world and mathematical problems.",
          "I can write, evaluate, and rewrite algebraic expressions in different forms to reveal relationships between quantities."
